snippet.textDisplay:
Lyrics ;)

Baatein teri karte hue
Thak ke so jaati hoon sirhaane aasmaan
Jaane kahaan mud jaati hain
Dekhte dekhte tujhe ye galiyan

Teri tarah khushbu chale..
Taare hamari tarah raaton se mile

Suni naheen zamaane ne teri meri kahaaniyan
Karde koyi nawaazishen karam mehrbaniyan

Yeh aarzu thi ki dekhe ye duniya
Ham jaisa koi deewaana hi naheen

Karde koyi nawaazishen karam mehrbaaniyaan

Raat andheri mein chhup rahe the
Gum ek sawera dhoond rahe the
Sadiyon se jaise jaag rahe the
Pyar ko apne dhaanp rahe the

Phir gir pade
Koyi mila naa sahaara kya kare

Suni nahi zamaane ne teri meri kahaaniyaan

Tera woh pyaar yaad aayega
Bhoolega naa ye dil mera
Kya ho gaya socha na tha

Tera woh pyar, Tera woh pyar
Tera woh pyar, Tera woh pyar (x2)

Teri woh khamoshiyaan
Kah deti theen woh sabhi jo tu nah kah saki

Kaise bataati tujhe
Sharmaati thi main jaise
Aanchal mein jalta diya

Khoye kahaan mujh ko bataa...

Tera woh pyaar yaad aayega
Bhoolega nah yeh dil mera (x2)

Kya ho gaya socha na tha.....
